Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.39,Main,Yukako,0,0,0,,Those vengeful spirits \N need to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:37.22,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,I'd go insane if I was \N possessed for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:41.65,Main,Yukako,0,0,0,,Koichi, if a vengeful spirit ever \N tries to possess you, tell me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:44.62,Main,Yukako,0,0,0,,I'll free you from its curse! {Does it count if you put another curse in its place?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.78,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Uh... Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.62,Main,Koichi,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:22:00.09,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,To this day, \N I'm unaware as to what became of that man. {added "as to" -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:07.11,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,Perhaps in a year or two \N I'll go on another research trip and see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:10.97,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,Staying vigilant even while \N possessed by vengeful spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:14.06,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,He's lived a lonely and proactive life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:19.53,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,Though I regard him as despicable,\N I find myself respecting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:23.60,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,Be that as it may...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:25.73,Thoughts,Rohan,0,0,0,,...I might be alone in thinking that.
